{"lang":"zh","stage":5,"title":"everyday sentences, growing","sentences":[{"t":"我不知道我在哪儿。","en":"I don't know where I am.","r":"Wǒ bù zhīdào wǒ zài nǎr.","a":"n_9b875fd03b69.mp3"},{"t":"我不知道它在哪儿。","en":"I don't know where it is.","r":"Wǒ bù zhīdào tā zài nǎr.","a":"n_1648880a430a.mp3"},{"t":"她是哪里人？","en":"Where is she from?","r":"Tā shì nǎlǐ rén?","a":"n_0af9a21ee357.mp3"},{"t":"我快迟到了。","en":"I'm running late.","r":"Wǒ kuài chídào le.","a":"n_a6ee5c2a4f21.mp3"},{"t":"有点疼。","en":"It hurts a little.","r":"Yǒudiǎn téng.","a":"n_a24424bf504e.mp3"},{"t":"哪儿都不疼。","en":"Nothing hurts.","r":"Nǎr dōu bù téng.","a":"n_a2a8aeb0c8c8.mp3"},{"t":"我今天没空。","en":"I don't have time today.","r":"Wǒ jīntiān méi kòng.","a":"n_0c3eef037c8d.mp3"},{"t":"我不是本地人。","en":"I'm not from here.","r":"Wǒ bú shì běndì rén.","a":"n_de430a2f81e2.mp3"},{"t":"我不知道该做什么。","en":"I don't know what to do.","r":"Wǒ bù zhīdào gāi zuò shénme.","a":"n_feae41f3943b.mp3"},{"t":"我有点累。","en":"I'm a little tired.","r":"Wǒ yǒudiǎn lèi.","a":"n_9a49ec511291.mp3"},{"t":"我今天真的好累。","en":"I'm really tired today.","r":"Wǒ jīntiān zhēn de hǎo lèi.","a":"n_39957355e45e.mp3"},{"t":"我喜欢你家。","en":"I like your house.","r":"Wǒ xǐhuan nǐ jiā.","a":"n_0b9e741bce22.mp3"},{"t":"今天我什么都不做。","en":"Today I'm doing nothing.","r":"Jīntiān wǒ shénme dōu bú zuò.","a":"n_63cce1a189ea.mp3"},{"t":"所有事都是我自己做。","en":"I do everything by myself.","r":"Suǒyǒu shì dōu shì wǒ zìjǐ zuò.","a":"n_6ed38a54481c.mp3"},{"t":"你别那么做。","en":"You don't do that.","r":"Nǐ bié nàme zuò.","a":"n_0a2b1180b451.mp3"},{"t":"我想回家。","en":"I want to go home.","r":"Wǒ xiǎng huíjiā.","a":"n_2d648aaa4383.mp3"},{"t":"今天星期几？","en":"What day is it today?","r":"Jīntiān xīngqī jǐ?","a":"n_8edc304656e0.mp3"},{"t":"我想买杯咖啡。","en":"I want to buy a coffee.","r":"Wǒ xiǎng mǎi bēi kāfēi.","a":"n_2e21ff5c3c0b.mp3"},{"t":"你今天想做什么？","en":"What do you want to do today?","r":"Nǐ jīntiān xiǎng zuò shénme?","a":"n_212a857f801d.mp3"},{"t":"我们去吃点东西吧。","en":"Let's go eat something.","r":"Wǒmen qù chī diǎn dōngxi ba.","a":"n_06c4cbc4101f.mp3"},{"t":"他不是我朋友。","en":"He's not my friend.","r":"Tā bú shì wǒ péngyou.","a":"n_407f505a561b.mp3"},{"t":"他是我朋友。","en":"He's my friend.","r":"Tā shì wǒ péngyou.","a":"n_aa6be2c4661e.mp3"},{"t":"这是我朋友。","en":"This is my friend.","r":"Zhè shì wǒ péngyou.","a":"n_a392593f964e.mp3"},{"t":"饭是我做的。","en":"I make the food.","r":"Fàn shì wǒ zuò de.","a":"n_984bae2b5cdf.mp3"},{"t":"菜怎么样？","en":"How's the food?","r":"Cài zěnmeyàng?","a":"n_84baf88e4ff0.mp3"},{"t":"这些一共多少钱？","en":"How much is all of this?","r":"Zhèxiē yígòng duōshao qián?","a":"n_a838134f6d84.mp3"},{"t":"坐公交多少钱？","en":"How much is the bus?","r":"Zuò gōngjiāo duōshao qián?","a":"n_ec3d7a5d7688.mp3"},{"t":"我不太舒服。","en":"I don't feel well.","r":"Wǒ bú tài shūfu.","a":"n_2d1e2a3d3f05.mp3"},{"t":"我现在好多了。","en":"I feel better now.","r":"Wǒ xiànzài hǎoduō le.","a":"n_c7afce8c52bc.mp3"},{"t":"那你是谁？","en":"And who are you?","r":"Nà nǐ shì shéi?","a":"n_eb95d8fd52c2.mp3"},{"t":"公交快到了。","en":"The bus is close.","r":"Gōngjiāo kuài dào le.","a":"n_c81f0e42e5b9.mp3"},{"t":"我今天钱不多。","en":"I have a little money today.","r":"Wǒ jīntiān qián bù duō.","a":"n_78c162d36931.mp3"},{"t":"那可是好多钱。","en":"That's a lot of money.","r":"Nà kěshì hǎoduō qián.","a":"n_24486adbbae0.mp3"},{"t":"有什么吃的？","en":"What is there to eat?","r":"Yǒu shénme chī de?","a":"n_690cf5d8fc5a.mp3"},{"t":"你到底去不去？","en":"Are you going or not?","r":"Nǐ dàodǐ qù bu qù?","a":"n_57606eaddb6f.mp3"},{"t":"我今天什么都没做。","en":"I didn't do anything today.","r":"Wǒ jīntiān shénme dōu méi zuò.","a":"n_fe561e3dea2c.mp3"},{"t":"昨天我什么都没做。","en":"Yesterday I did nothing.","r":"Zuótiān wǒ shénme dōu méi zuò.","a":"n_1f12b41a13bb.mp3"},{"t":"我昨天什么都没做。","en":"I didn't do anything yesterday.","r":"Wǒ zuótiān shénme dōu méi zuò.","a":"n_6f074ad284cd.mp3"},{"t":"我在厨房。","en":"I'm in the kitchen.","r":"Wǒ zài chúfáng.","a":"n_28b1ad241855.mp3"},{"t":"厨房在这儿。","en":"The kitchen is here.","r":"Chúfáng zài zhèr.","a":"n_15520703c585.mp3"},{"t":"厨房在哪儿？","en":"Where's the kitchen?","r":"Chúfáng zài nǎr?","a":"n_88ffa4bc65ca.mp3"},{"t":"医生在哪儿？","en":"Where's the doctor?","r":"Yīshēng zài nǎr?","a":"n_30717dc0b431.mp3"},{"t":"我今天去看医生。","en":"I'm going to the doctor today.","r":"Wǒ jīntiān qù kàn yīshēng.","a":"n_aecb2bf4ad8b.mp3"},{"t":"我得去看医生。","en":"I need to go to the doctor.","r":"Wǒ děi qù kàn yīshēng.","a":"n_2895bf60acff.mp3"},{"t":"我真的很不舒服。","en":"I feel really bad.","r":"Wǒ zhēn de hěn bù shūfu.","a":"n_9ded088760e3.mp3"},{"t":"我想要杯咖啡。","en":"I'd like a coffee.","r":"Wǒ xiǎng yào bēi kāfēi.","a":"n_d68359b29644.mp3"},{"t":"我手机在哪儿？","en":"Where's my phone?","r":"Wǒ shǒujī zài nǎr?","a":"n_5bfd30cb3a72.mp3"},{"t":"我看不太清你。","en":"I can't see you well.","r":"Wǒ kàn bu tài qīng nǐ.","a":"n_f5b9c1580751.mp3"},{"t":"待会儿见。","en":"I'll see you later.","r":"Dāihuìr jiàn.","a":"n_ee22f5a1c6d7.mp3"},{"t":"今天我起晚了。","en":"Today I'm getting up late.","r":"Jīntiān wǒ qǐ wǎn le.","a":"n_ddf58610bf86.mp3"},{"t":"明天我早起。","en":"Tomorrow I'm getting up early.","r":"Míngtiān wǒ zǎoqǐ.","a":"n_81377917d35f.mp3"},{"t":"我不知道点什么。","en":"I don't know what to order.","r":"Wǒ bù zhīdào diǎn shénme.","a":"n_3eb09cd5d6b4.mp3"},{"t":"你要点什么？","en":"What are you going to order?","r":"Nǐ yào diǎn shénme?","a":"n_074f6883dcc4.mp3"},{"t":"我好想睡觉。","en":"I feel like sleeping.","r":"Wǒ hǎo xiǎng shuìjiào.","a":"n_2299ac126292.mp3"},{"t":"你想出去吗？","en":"Do you feel like going out?","r":"Nǐ xiǎng chūqù ma?","a":"n_4eabd1ffe1fe.mp3"},{"t":"水多少钱？","en":"How much is the water?","r":"Shuǐ duōshao qián?","a":"n_a07fa48f0cfb.mp3"},{"t":"我们在厨房。","en":"We're in the kitchen.","r":"Wǒmen zài chúfáng.","a":"n_10280679fb18.mp3"},{"t":"我想多学点。","en":"I'd like to learn more.","r":"Wǒ xiǎng duō xué diǎn.","a":"n_28690447a778.mp3"},{"t":"你不该那么做。","en":"You shouldn't do that.","r":"Nǐ bù gāi nàme zuò.","a":"n_92dbee4339d2.mp3"},{"t":"你不该工作那么多。","en":"You shouldn't work so much.","r":"Nǐ bù gāi gōngzuò nàme duō.","a":"n_684e6f7504ca.mp3"},{"t":"你为什么不来？","en":"Why aren't you coming?","r":"Nǐ wèishénme bù lái?","a":"n_c77c74adf280.mp3"},{"t":"你几点来？","en":"What time are you coming?","r":"Nǐ jǐ diǎn lái?","a":"n_28be4fd97f28.mp3"},{"t":"是近还是远？","en":"Is it close or far?","r":"Shì jìn háishi yuǎn?","a":"n_e6949e4d822a.mp3"},{"t":"火车很便宜。","en":"The train is cheap.","r":"Huǒchē hěn piányi.","a":"n_22b80c7b09e4.mp3"},{"t":"火车站很远。","en":"The train is far.","r":"Huǒchē zhàn hěn yuǎn.","a":"n_2d2cbeaa1983.mp3"},{"t":"有没有更便宜的？","en":"Do you have anything cheaper?","r":"Yǒu méiyǒu gèng piányi de?","a":"n_38e2035aabbe.mp3"},{"t":"又是我。","en":"It's me again.","r":"Yòu shì wǒ.","a":"n_737c4f82211e.mp3"},{"t":"我五分钟就到。","en":"I'll be there in five minutes.","r":"Wǒ wǔ fēnzhōng jiù dào.","a":"n_c4110fe6ca91.mp3"},{"t":"我喜欢跟你出去。","en":"I like going out with you.","r":"Wǒ xǐhuan gēn nǐ chūqù.","a":"n_59a11c64f39b.mp3"},{"t":"我想跟你一起去。","en":"I'd like to go with you.","r":"Wǒ xiǎng gēn nǐ yìqǐ qù.","a":"n_52a6278221f3.mp3"},{"t":"我想跟你一起学西班牙语。","en":"I want to learn Spanish with you.","r":"Wǒ xiǎng gēn nǐ yìqǐ xué Xībānyáyǔ.","a":"n_4eba60b9db60.mp3"},{"t":"明天我要学习。","en":"Tomorrow I'm going to study.","r":"Míngtiān wǒ yào xuéxí.","a":"n_94eb0ad99db4.mp3"},{"t":"没人跟我说过。","en":"Nobody told me anything.","r":"Méi rén gēn wǒ shuō guò.","a":"n_72e6677bcf8a.mp3"},{"t":"他什么时候跟你说的？","en":"When did he tell you?","r":"Tā shénme shíhou gēn nǐ shuō de?","a":"n_e9deb0a44bb0.mp3"},{"t":"疼多久了？","en":"How long has it been hurting?","r":"Téng duōjiǔ le?","a":"n_435a313aff84.mp3"},{"t":"我今天早点睡。","en":"I'm going to bed early today.","r":"Wǒ jīntiān zǎodiǎn shuì.","a":"n_2011896501ac.mp3"},{"t":"市中心怎么走？","en":"How do I get downtown?","r":"Shìzhōngxīn zěnme zǒu?","a":"n_173a20df0e11.mp3"},{"t":"你为什么难过？","en":"Why are you sad?","r":"Nǐ wèishénme nánguò?","a":"n_ff4e8163262a.mp3"},{"t":"他说我什么了？","en":"What did he say about me?","r":"Tā shuō wǒ shénme le?","a":"n_466808220b3f.mp3"},{"t":"我要一样的。","en":"I want the same thing.","r":"Wǒ yào yíyàng de.","a":"n_5c648aabcdeb.mp3"},{"t":"我能问个问题吗？","en":"Can I ask a question?","r":"Wǒ néng wèn ge wèntí ma?","a":"n_46a8f8639959.mp3"},{"t":"他老问一样的问题。","en":"He always asks the same thing.","r":"Tā lǎo wèn yíyàng de wèntí.","a":"n_60fefce5e1f1.mp3"},{"t":"谁在打听我？","en":"Who's asking about me?","r":"Shéi zài dǎtīng wǒ?","a":"n_357146b54049.mp3"},{"t":"我不知道说什么好。","en":"I don't know what to say.","r":"Wǒ bù zhīdào shuō shénme hǎo.","a":"n_76b651fec3a3.mp3"},{"t":"我今天不健身。","en":"I'm not working out today.","r":"Wǒ jīntiān bú jiànshēn.","a":"n_13a713d58416.mp3"},{"t":"我想多健身。","en":"I want to work out more.","r":"Wǒ xiǎng duō jiànshēn.","a":"n_cc039bf2f13f.mp3"},{"t":"你认识我朋友吗？","en":"Do you know my friend?","r":"Nǐ rènshi wǒ péngyou ma?","a":"n_df353386b6b0.mp3"},{"t":"我现在就去付钱。","en":"I'm going to pay now.","r":"Wǒ xiànzài jiù qù fùqián.","a":"n_fd45ac97c09a.mp3"},{"t":"我不想付那么多。","en":"I don't want to pay that much.","r":"Wǒ bù xiǎng fù nàme duō.","a":"n_a070a0a73172.mp3"},{"t":"出租车到了。","en":"The taxi is here.","r":"Chūzūchē dào le.","a":"n_17404a911748.mp3"},{"t":"我十分钟就到。","en":"I'll be there in ten minutes.","r":"Wǒ shí fēnzhōng jiù dào.","a":"n_d9b0093650ad.mp3"},{"t":"我十点到。","en":"I arrive at ten.","r":"Wǒ shí diǎn dào.","a":"n_7b05eb39510b.mp3"},{"t":"那不是我的名字。","en":"That's not my name.","r":"Nà bú shì wǒ de míngzi.","a":"n_e086dd8cc8e3.mp3"},{"t":"我去参加派对。","en":"I'm going to the party.","r":"Wǒ qù cānjiā pàiduì.","a":"n_d98c9333e8e7.mp3"}]}